Since PvP server we are not.<br>
May have already been done or attempted…<br>
<br>
I think it would be an awesome event to have 6 of a guilds top players (representatives) go of at each other in a tournament. Yeah, it’s a good thing to have a Guild be the first at a MOB. Basically all your doing is finding a strategy to kill it and then most of the time re-execute the strategy that works for you (Farm the crap and quest to get at it). If you really want to know who is the best guild, which has better tactics, Skill, gear yada yada yada. Go head to head with each other.<br>
I think this would spawn interest, excitement, bragging rights and of course rivalry. It would be much harder to defeat an enemy that THINKS rather than one that has a pretty much predictable reaction. If the prestige is not enough, then a loot item or zone rights, as a trophy would be nice. Would also be nice a GM Artifact as a trophy that must be transferred to the winning team (err, maybe not).<br>
<br>
All this especially when most peeps that are still here or have retired are already 60 and bored out of their minds…<br>
